data.description: This four bedroom home is in really good condition with a wrap around deck that is so pleasing and relaxing for the outdoors family. Home has newer central heat and air unit one and a half year old. New siding, all new appliances and much more. The down stairs master is large and at present being used as a den, it has its own bath and walk in closet along with another closet. upstairs there is another large bedroom with two other nice size bedroom and a bath. home has been well keep and in excellent shape laundry room is off the kitchen. the open floor plan  include the kitchen living room and dining room combo. The lot goes back 671.56 feet for an acre of land, not all is cleared. seller is offering a one year home warranty and is open for offers. all bedrooms have double closet space.
